title: FC CeBra 01
text: Football Club Cessange Bracarenses Grund 2001 is a <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> <a href="football%20club">club</a>, based in <a href="Cessange">Cessange</a>, in southern <a href="Luxembourg">Luxembourg</a> founded in 2001 after a merger between Progrès Cessange and Bracarenses Grund.
